acceptance_criteria: Golden transcript corpus (canonical agent task sequences) versioned in-repo; replay runner reports bytes+approx-tokens per completed task against the current build; wired into the existing token-cost CI gate lineage with a documented regression threshold; boundary with pm-atfm quality harness documented; workflow for adding transcripts documented
